acceptable solutions of the problem."
</P>
<P>
However, the Belarussian authorities will not impose sanctions
on European Union member nations that have decided not to issue
visas to Belarussian senior officials, Lukashenko said.
</P>
<P>
The president stated that Belarus may renounce Western
assistance in physical rehabilitation of children affected by the
Chernobyl nuclear disaster, if Western countries continue to
discriminate against Belarussian citizens who want to visit
European countries.  
