important part of Liberty Mutual's future business in China. He
noted that Chongqing is the economic center and major inland river
port in southwest China and the upper reaches of the Yangtze River.
</P>
<P>
Some 100 foreign insurance institutions from 15 countries and
regions have opened representative offices in China, with branches
of nine overseas companies currently operating in the country.
</P>
<P>
China now has 30 insurance companies, and the 1997 national
premium income reached 108 billion yuan, up 39.3 percent from the
1996 figure.  
