quoting eye witnesses, said the detainees are neither allowed to
leave Assab nor work there and that some have to report every day
to Eritrea's governing party, the Eritrean People's Liberation
Front (EPLF). (Ethiopia-Eritrea)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
