<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, July 14 (Xinhua) -- International Olympic Committee
President Juan Samaranch on Tuesday awarded Moscow Mayor Yuri
Luzhkov a Golden Olympic Order to commend his contributions to
world sports.
</P>
<P>
At a ceremony held on the central square of the Olympic village
of the World Youth Games, Samaranch praised the organizers for the
grand opening ceremony the previous evening in the Luzhniki
Stadium.
</P>
