hopes to win the rights to host the 2012 summer Olympics. It was
venue of the 1980 Olympiad.
</P>
<P>
Luzhkov, for his part, thanked the IOC for the honor and
pledged to do his best to promote the Olympic spirit and youth
sports in Moscow and Russia.
</P>
<P>
After the ceremony, Samaranch toured the Olympic village.
